This is a multiple dose, randomized, parallel, double-blind, double-dummy, multicenter and multinational Phase III study to determine the efficacy and safety of Aclidinium bromide 4001/2g/Formoterol Fumarate (AB/FF) 12 1/2g compared to individual components and TIO (Tiotropium) 18 1/2g when administered to patients with stable chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD).

